{"tid":843371,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲格復出教波即捧盃　曼迷叫曼聯諗諗佢","createTime":"2018-10-01T06:02:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T06:21:22.000Z","uid":54373,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"07dc2f26aa34ee0a075c97b3b1c8f81f7994fa00","tid":843371,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T06:02:55.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴傳奇領隊雲格今夏結束「兵工廠」執教生涯後，近期似乎開始波癮發作，頻頻出席足球賽事。雲格日前接受尼日利亞名將簡尼邀請，喺「簡奴盃」慈善賽擔任英超明星隊主帥，對手係非洲明星隊。<br />\n<br />\n英超明星隊以前阿仙奴球員為主，包括列文、皮利斯、蘇甘保、加拿斯等等，至於非洲明星隊就有高路托尼、耶高保、艾摩卡治、迪贊巴、羅倫同美度等球星，最終英超明星隊大勝9比4，雲格亦成功捧走「簡奴盃」冠軍。曼聯依家盛傳將會炒莫連奴，唔少網民就抵死留言，叫曼聯高層不如考慮下搵雲格執教喎！"},{"pid":"fd817d46d2b586e25a59b38065945da12059b0c7","tid":843371,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T06:06:51.000Z","msg":"快"},{"pid":"bc4ebfc719e53e61f5548b67ca32a3d153a3a5b6","tid":843371,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T06:07:13.000Z","msg":"阿迷會點諗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1ec346a16222ebc355180d8a858811b53c5ecd2","tid":843371,"uid":39974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T06:17:39.000Z","msg":"爺爺又贏"},{"pid":"d5dcacc62e91253b7cda9f5f3b1238a9ad92e9c9","tid":843371,"uid":146435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T06:19:12.000Z","msg":"又拎飛機盃"},{"pid":"4ba6e49dfca2a17268af5e5a441363c9f179f98f","tid":843371,"uid":94824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T06:19:50.000Z","msg":"山神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0012ba8a1b8d0dfbb4946dca0a7bdb45428a2628","tid":843371,"uid":59283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T06:19:58.000Z","msg":"離開阿狗嘅下場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08810d471459ee286dd23e042ed7e92330a820c1","tid":843371,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T06:21:22.000Z","msg